01:29:21,500 --> 01:29:22,800
fait. . .

761
01:29:23,100 --> 01:29:24,700
avec. . .

762
01:29:27,800 --> 01:29:29,500
conte de fées.

763
01:29:34,100 --> 01:29:35,300
Maintenant. . .

764
01:29:36,300 --> 01:29:37,900
demande-lui à nouveau.

765
01:29:46,400 --> 01:29:47,600
Comment. . .

766
01:29:48,600 --> 01:29:50,800
